'''天主教特魯希略總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Truxillensis}}；{{lang-es|Arquidiócesis de Trujillo}}）是[[秘魯|秘魯]]的一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省[[總教區|總教區]]，下轄六個教區，是該國七個總教區之一。

教區於1577年4月15日成立，1943年5月23日升為總教區<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=X |year=1943 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=273-275 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-35-1943-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404122816/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-35-1943-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-04 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

總教區管轄[[拉利伯塔德大區|拉利伯塔德大區]]九省，2006年時有教友1,149,000人（佔轄區總人口83.6%）、六十九個堂區和126名司鐸。現任總主教為{{link-es|彌額爾·卡夫雷霍斯-维达特|Miguel Cabrejos Vidarte}}，輔理主教為{{link-de|弟茂德·索洛爾桑諾-羅哈斯|Timoteo Solórzano Rojas}}和{{link-de|方濟各·卡斯特羅-拉盧普|Francisco Castro Lalupú}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 06.11.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/11/06/181106b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716061925/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/11/06/181106b.html |archivedate=2019-07-16 |language=en |date=2018-11-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 04.04.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/04/200404b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-04-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404133142/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/04/200404b.html |archivedate=2020-04-04 |language=en |date=2020-04-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

